OL,3,CMohamed Salah to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cend of season
OL,6,FMohamed Salah is set to leave
OL,7,FLiverpool at the end of this season,
OL,8,Fthe Premier League club have announced.
OL,10,FThe 33-year-old arrived at Anfield
OL,11,Ffrom Roma in 2017 and has made 435
OL,12,Fappearances for Liverpool, scoring 255
OL,13,Fgoals.
OL,15,FA statement on the official Liverpool
OL,16,Fwebsite said: "Mohamed Salah is to
OL,17,Fbring the curtain down on his
OL,18,Fillustrious career with Liverpool at
OL,19,Fthe end of the 2025-26 season.
OL,26,@xD@OOU
