OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774469469
OL,3,CMohamed Salah to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cend of season
OL,6,F"The forward has reached an agreement
OL,7,Fwith the Reds that will see him close
OL,8,Fa remarkable nine-year chapter at
OL,9,FAnfield.
OL,11,F"Salah expressed his wish to make this
OL,12,Fannouncement to the supporters at the
OL,13,Fearliest possible opportunity to
OL,14,Fprovide transparency about his future
OL,15,Fdue to his respect and gratitude for
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,18,FIn a video featuring highlights of his
OL,19,Ftime with Liverpool posted on X, Salah
OL,20,Fsaid: "Hello everyone. Unfortunately,
OL,21,Fthe day has come.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@FO]|D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
