CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774469469
OL,3,CMohamed Salah to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cend of season
OL,6,F"This is the first part of my
OL,7,Ffarewell. I will be leaving Liverpool
OL,8,Fat the end of the season.
OL,10,F"I wanted to start by saying that I
OL,11,Fnever imagined how deeply this club,
OL,12,Fthis city, these people would become
OL,13,Fpart of my life. Liverpool is not just
OL,14,Fa football club. It's a passion, it's
OL,15,Fa history, it's a spirit. I can't
OL,16,Fexplain in words to anyone not of this
OL,17,Fclub.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
