PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774469469
OL,3,CMohamed Salah to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cend of season
OL,6,F"We celebrated victory, we won the
OL,7,Fmost important trophies and we fought
OL,8,Ftogether through the hardest time in
OL,9,Four life. I want to thank everyone who
OL,10,Fwas part of this club throughout my
OL,11,Ftime here, especially the team-mates
OL,12,Fpast and present.
OL,14,F"And to the fans, I don't have enough
OL,15,Fwords. The support you showed me
OL,16,Fthrough the best time of my career,
OL,17,Fand you stood by me in the toughest
OL,18,Ftimes. It's something I will never
OL,19,Fforget and something I will take with
OL,20,Fme always.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
