OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774469469
OL,3,CMohamed Salah to leave Liverpool at
OL,4,Cend of season
OL,6,F"Leaving is never easy. You gave me
OL,7,Fthe best time of my life. I will be
OL,8,Falways one of you. This club will
OL,9,Falways be my home, to me and to my
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,F"Thank you for everything. Because of
OL,13,Fall of you, I will never walk alone."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@eO]
